text: Bannister is an unincorporated community in Camden County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Bannister was established in 1893, and remained in operation until 1916. The community most likely was named after the Bannister family. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Camden County, Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Bannister, Missouri
